com.xceptance.xlt.common.util.action.execution

Interface URLActionDataExecutionable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    HtmlPageAction, LightWeightPageAction, XhrHtmlPageAction, XhrLightWeightPageAction

    public interface URLActionDataExecutionable
    A simple interface for the execution of a http request.
    the response must be wrapped with a URLActionDataExecutableResult.
    Author:
    matthias mitterreiter
